      <title>南非议长未能停止逮捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/south-africa-speaker-loses-bid-to-stop-arrest-over-alleged-graft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非议会议长诺西维韦·马皮萨-恩卡库拉 (Nosiviwe Mapisa-Nqakula) 在阻止当局因腐败指控而拘留她的法庭诉讼中败诉，目前面临逮捕。]]></description>
